Display All Commits
      git log --all

View recent 2 commits
      git log -2

Filter commit by author
      git log --author <name>
      git log --committer <name>

Filter commits by X days
      git log --before <date>
      git log --after <date>
      git log --after 2.days.ago

View by date range
      git log --after <date>  --before <date>
      git log --after "2014-02-01" --before "2014-02-02"

View all diff for changes for each commit
      git log -p

view summary for each commit
      git log --stat

view one line for each commit
      git log --oneline
